data.description: Welcome to your mountain retreat or permanent home in beautiful Idyllwild! Nature lovers will adore this property, nestled near the South Ridge Trail with easy access to town. The well-maintained home boasts a spacious driveway for ample parking or a potential garage addition. Outside, enjoy gatherings by the custom fire pit or cozy up in the jacuzzi on chilly evenings. Inside, rustic charm abounds with natural wood accents, a brick fireplace, and built-in cabinetry, offering generous storage throughout. Sold fully furnished!
